comments: I really enjoyed the HIT but it took me a moment to realize I should choose all of the like items (I think). Really fun regardless :)

I second guessed myself at various points about how inclusive I should be when there were slight variations in design (ie, a flat front school bus versus a regular school bus), but I suppose that was the point of the experiment.

This was an interesting and fun HIT! Some of the last few picks though did confuse me as they were different words corresponding to the same pictures/objects that earlier in the survey had different words attributed to them. I thought about not picking any of them for that reason, but didn't know if that was an option or would be seen as not completing it correctly... so I just went with what my intuition felt was correct in making my choices.

Thank you for the opportunity to participate. Have a nice day!
